## Description

Recently, while building https://github.com/lexicalunit/nanodbc library which uses Catch using MinGW-W64 5.3.0, the following error is thrown:

```
In file included from C:/projects/nanodbc/catch/src/catch/include/internal/catch_run_context.hpp:23:0,
                 from C:/projects/nanodbc/catch/src/catch/include/catch_session.hpp:13,
                 from C:/projects/nanodbc/catch/src/catch/include/internal/catch_impl.hpp:19,
                 from C:/projects/nanodbc/catch/src/catch/include/catch.hpp:53,
                 from C:\projects\nanodbc\test\main.cpp:2:
C:/projects/nanodbc/catch/src/catch/include/internal/catch_fatal_condition.hpp: In member function 'void Catch::FatalConditionHandler::reset()':
C:/projects/nanodbc/catch/src/catch/include/internal/catch_fatal_condition.hpp:72:71: error: invalid conversion from 'LONG (__attribute__((__stdcall__)) *)(PEXCEPTION_POINTERS) {aka long int (__attribute__((__stdcall__)) *)(_EXCEPTION_POINTERS*)}' to 'PVOID {aka void*}' [-fpermissive]
                 RemoveVectoredExceptionHandler(handleVectoredException);
                                                                       ^
In file included from C:/mingw-w64/i686-5.3.0-posix-dwarf-rt_v4-rev0/mingw32/i686-w64-mingw32/include/winbase.h:16:0,
                 from C:/mingw-w64/i686-5.3.0-posix-dwarf-rt_v4-rev0/mingw32/i686-w64-mingw32/include/windows.h:70,
                 from C:/projects/nanodbc/catch/src/catch/include/internal/catch_fatal_condition.hpp:28,
                 from C:/projects/nanodbc/catch/src/catch/include/internal/catch_run_context.hpp:23,
                 from C:/projects/nanodbc/catch/src/catch/include/catch_session.hpp:13,
                 from C:/projects/nanodbc/catch/src/catch/include/internal/catch_impl.hpp:19,
                 from C:/projects/nanodbc/catch/src/catch/include/catch.hpp:53,
                 from C:\projects\nanodbc\test\main.cpp:2:
C:/mingw-w64/i686-5.3.0-posix-dwarf-rt_v4-rev0/mingw32/i686-w64-mingw32/include/errhandlingapi.h:24:27: note:   initializing argument 1 of 'ULONG RemoveVectoredExceptionHandler(PVOID)'
   WINBASEAPI ULONG WINAPI RemoveVectoredExceptionHandler (PVOID Handle);
```

Full [build log on AppVeyor](https://ci.appveyor.com/project/lexicalunit/nanodbc/branch/master/job/y0oh51erjm3fbe9e)


### Extra information
<!--
Fill in any extra information that might be important for your issue.

If your issue is a bugreport, definitely fill out at least the following.
-->
* Catch version: **v1.6.1**  (latest master branch at 615aa071a8f741862c325e0aab47345cc5388169)
* Operating System: Windows on AppVeyor CI
* Compiler+version: MinGW-W64 5.3.0
